ğŸ§­ Dashboard Overview

This dashboard provides an end-to-end analysis of the Brazilian Olist e-commerce platform, focusing on revenue performance, customer behavior, seller contribution, product categories, payment methods, and logistics impact.
All metrics are calculated using delivered orders only to ensure business accuracy.

ğŸ”‘ Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)

Total Revenue: R$ 19.77M

Total Orders: 96,455 delivered orders

Average Order Value (AOV): R$ 204.99

Total Customers: 96,455 unique customers

These KPIs summarize the overall health and scale of marketplace activity.

ğŸ“ˆ Revenue Trend Analysis

The monthly revenue trend shows consistent growth over time, reflecting increasing platform adoption.
Seasonal spikes are visible in certain months, indicating periodic demand surges and promotional effects.

Insight:
Revenue closely follows order volume, suggesting a stable average order value across the analysis period.

ğŸ’³ Payment Method Analysis

Credit cards are the dominant payment method, contributing approximately 77% of total revenue, followed by boleto and debit cards.

Business Insight:
Customers strongly prefer flexible payment options, making credit card support critical for revenue growth.

